---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — Thanarak Kanyaprasit">
  <main class="legal">
    <article class="legal-inner">
      <header>
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: May 26, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how this application ("we", "our", or
          "the App") collects, uses, and protects information when you use it.
          By using the App, you agree to the practices described below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you authenticate via Facebook Login, we may receive:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your public profile (name, profile picture, Facebook ID)</li>
          <li>Email address (only if you grant permission)</li>
          <li>Any additional data scopes you explicitly approve</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not collect sensitive personal information beyond what is
          necessary to operate the App.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To authenticate and identify you within the App</li>
          <li>To personalize your experience</li>
          <li>To improve and maintain the App</li>
          <li>To communicate important updates if you opt in</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We may share
          limited data with trusted service providers strictly to operate the
          App, or when required by law.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your information only as long as your account is active or
          as needed to provide the service. You may request deletion at any
          time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Revoke Facebook permissions from your Facebook settings</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          To request deletion of your data, email
          <a href="mailto:kin491512@gmail.com">kin491512@gmail.com</a>
          with the subject "Data Deletion Request". We will process the request
          within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Security</h2>
        <p>
          We apply reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect
          your information. No method of transmission over the Internet is 100%
          secure, however, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          The App is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly
          collect data from children under 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be
          posted on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>11. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact:<br />
          <a href="mailto:kin491512@gmail.com">kin491512@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="legal-foot">
        <a href="/">← Back to home</a>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem) clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--ink, #f4f1ea);
    background: var(--bg, #0d0c0a);
  }

  .legal-inner {
    max-width: 72ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: "Hanken Grotesk", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.2vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.55;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 1.5rem + 4vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .updated {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin: 0 0 3.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  p,
  ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    opacity: 0.82;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  li {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 200ms ease;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: currentColor;
  }

  .legal-foot {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
</style>
